[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]a)
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]‘consumer accountability’, e.g. strengthen consumer responsiveness and market position, foster school competition and market branding/impact.
[normal]b)
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]‘
[normal]performative
[normal] accountability’, e.g. performance management, responsiveness to arms-length regulatory bodies, targets, indicators and evaluations.
[normal]c)
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]‘corporate accountability’, e.g. strengthen service efficiency, value for money, competitive tendering, emphasis on school survival, adaptability and flexibility.
